01:35.228 --> 01:36.662
- No!

01:36.664 --> 01:37.629
- Hey, mom.

01:38.766 --> 01:39.665
Mom?

01:41.601 --> 01:42.801
Mom?

01:42.803 --> 01:45.204
Mom, oh my god, mom!

02:21.074 --> 02:23.275
- Thanks for coming.

02:23.277 --> 02:24.543
They're frying me
in the morning,

02:24.545 --> 02:26.278
so my time is short.

02:29.682 --> 02:31.350
- What is it you need from me

02:31.352 --> 02:32.951
at this late hour?

02:32.953 --> 02:32.951
Salvation?

02:34.821 --> 02:36.355
- I'll take that up
with the almighty

02:36.357 --> 02:38.423
when I see him tomorrow.

02:40.727 --> 02:42.528
I need to tell you...

02:44.130 --> 02:46.198
- Tell me what, Charles?

02:47.767 --> 02:51.170
- Something made me
kill my family.

02:51.172 --> 02:52.504
Something evil.

02:54.407 --> 02:58.143
And it was something i
brought home with me.

02:59.779 --> 03:03.282
- Many things drive
people to do what they do.

03:03.284 --> 03:05.517
I'm not here to judge you.

03:07.420 --> 03:09.922
- It was something evil.

03:09.924 --> 03:11.957
I'm a contractor by trade and

03:11.959 --> 03:14.026
I worked at that house.

03:14.028 --> 03:16.929
You know, the famous one?

03:16.931 --> 03:19.064
The haunted one?

03:19.066 --> 03:21.900
- That house has been cleansed
for years.

03:21.902 --> 03:26.972
The current owners haven't
reported any phenomenon.

03:26.974 --> 03:29.708
- I was there before
all that hub bub.

03:29.710 --> 03:31.410
Before the priest
was killed exorcising

03:31.412 --> 03:33.045
the demons from it?

03:34.547 --> 03:35.447
- Yes.

03:36.249 --> 03:39.218
I'm familiar with the incident.

03:39.220 --> 03:40.986
Very familiar.

03:40.988 --> 03:41.887
- Ah!

03:45.792 --> 03:50.128
- I was there for weeks,
renovating a room.

03:50.130 --> 03:52.431
When I left, I took some
of the original lumber

03:52.433 --> 03:54.499
with me for another project.

03:59.806 --> 04:02.641
And that's when it took me over,

04:02.643 --> 04:06.044
when I brought
the materials home.

04:06.046 --> 04:08.947
I should have left them
in that accursed place.

04:08.949 --> 04:11.083
- You took the lumber home

04:11.085 --> 04:13.685
and that's when you
say you were possessed?

04:13.687 --> 04:17.122
- Dammit, I'm not saying, I was,

04:17.124 --> 04:19.291
and that's why
i want you to know,

04:19.293 --> 04:19.291
so you can go
to the last place that

04:19.293 --> 04:24.763
I worked and help those
people if they need it.

04:24.765 --> 04:26.031
I don't want anyone
going through

04:26.033 --> 04:28.767
the hell that I've gone through.

04:42.215 --> 04:43.982
Oh, for god's sake, say
something.

04:45.252 --> 04:47.386
Time's up, father.

04:56.095 --> 04:58.897
- Evil moves
just like people do.

05:01.534 --> 05:02.601
- Thank you.

05:03.970 --> 05:07.806
Maybe in some small way
I've redeemed myself.

05:09.108 --> 05:13.078
- Maybe you have, my son,
maybe you have.

05:16.517 --> 05:19.985
- Maybe I'll see ya
up there.

05:19.987 --> 05:20.952
- Possibly.

05:22.422 --> 05:23.422
Good night.

09:45.017 --> 09:45.917
- Ah!

10:12.211 --> 10:14.079
- I don't like
that kid!

10:14.081 --> 10:16.381
- You don't like
any of my friends.

10:16.383 --> 10:17.983
- I don't like him!

10:17.985 --> 10:19.250
He's your boyfriend, right?

10:19.252 --> 10:20.986
- You
think every guy I talk to

10:20.988 --> 10:22.287
is my boyfriend.

10:22.289 --> 10:24.389
We're friends, that's it.

10:24.391 --> 10:26.057
- You better watch it, missy.

10:26.059 --> 10:28.793
- You're just jealous because
you don't have any friends.

10:28.795 --> 10:29.828
- Watch it.

10:29.830 --> 10:29.828
- It's true.

10:29.830 --> 10:34.566
Who'd wanna be friends
with a, a stinking drunk?

10:34.568 --> 10:36.635
That's right,
go ahead and hit me

10:36.637 --> 10:39.404
like you did to mom when
she got on your case.

10:59.325 --> 11:00.225
- Hello?

11:01.027 --> 11:02.494
- Hey, robby.

11:02.496 --> 11:04.629
- Amy, how's it goin'?

11:04.631 --> 11:05.930
- Not too good.

11:07.166 --> 11:08.199
- Oh, boy.

11:08.201 --> 11:09.868
Another fight with your dad?

11:09.870 --> 11:12.504
- Yeah, this time a bad one.

11:12.506 --> 11:15.240
- Okay, tell me about it.

11:15.242 --> 11:19.778
- He's just always on my
case about everything.

11:19.780 --> 11:22.313
And he started
drinking heavily again.

11:22.315 --> 11:24.549
- He didn't hit you again?

11:25.418 --> 11:27.686
- No, not this time.

11:27.688 --> 11:30.155
But he was mad enough
that he could have.

11:30.157 --> 11:31.890
I wish he were dead.

11:32.758 --> 11:34.459
- You don't mean that.

11:34.461 --> 11:35.527
- Yes, I do.

11:36.295 --> 11:39.130
The world would be
a better place.

11:39.132 --> 11:41.466
And I'd be better off, too.

11:44.036 --> 11:45.103
- I'm sorry.

11:46.739 --> 11:47.639
- Thanks.

13:15.961 --> 13:18.029
- The evil must be ridden
from the house.

13:18.031 --> 13:20.031
It's the only way.

13:20.033 --> 13:22.200
- To exorcise a house?

13:22.202 --> 13:26.104
It goes against our
vows, the church and god.

13:26.106 --> 13:27.939
- Fighting Satan and his legion
of evil

13:27.941 --> 13:30.608
is what we're called for.

13:30.610 --> 13:33.344
You can hide behind
the laws of the church,

13:33.346 --> 13:35.680
but this evil is a reality.

13:37.349 --> 13:39.384
What men of god are we
if we don't,

13:39.386 --> 13:42.053
in good faith, try and stop it?

13:43.622 --> 13:46.357
- Please brother, I beg you, no.

13:47.259 --> 13:49.093
- Then I'll do it myself.

13:49.095 --> 13:51.095
- You need permission
from the church!

13:51.097 --> 13:53.531
- I have permission from god.

13:53.533 --> 13:55.433
Are you with me or not?

13:55.435 --> 13:56.734
- I can't.

13:56.736 --> 13:58.303
You can't.

13:58.305 --> 14:00.872
- Someone has to do something.

14:00.874 --> 14:02.674
This can't go on.

14:02.676 --> 14:04.876
The lives that this darkness
has destroyed

14:04.878 --> 14:06.878
is only gonna multiply!

14:08.647 --> 14:09.547
- I can't.

14:10.316 --> 14:11.549
I'm sorry.

14:11.551 --> 14:12.951
God be with you.

14:14.987 --> 14:16.554
- God be with you.

14:19.960 --> 14:22.927
- I warned you to stay away.

14:22.929 --> 14:24.462
- No!

15:33.099 --> 15:34.399
- Who's there?

15:48.180 --> 15:49.080
Hello?

15:50.916 --> 15:51.816
Dad?

15:53.319 --> 15:54.385
Is that you?

16:44.703 --> 16:45.603
Figures.

17:01.653 --> 17:04.088
I know there's someone in here.

17:45.831 --> 17:48.066
Who the hell is down here?

17:52.137 --> 17:53.538
I can't see you,

17:55.340 --> 17:57.008
but I can hear you.

18:34.379 --> 18:35.279
Ah!

18:43.956 --> 18:45.289
- What's going on?

18:45.291 --> 18:48.159
- I heard a voice and so
i followed it down here

18:48.161 --> 18:49.994
and then I saw
something terrible!

18:49.996 --> 18:52.163
- Alright, alright,
it's alright.

18:52.165 --> 18:54.599
There's nothing
going on here now.

18:54.601 --> 18:55.967
Are you sure you weren't
daydreaming?

18:55.969 --> 18:57.568
- No.

18:57.570 --> 18:59.971
I don't, I don't think so.

18:59.973 --> 19:01.539
No.

19:01.541 --> 19:01.539
- Okay, alright.

19:01.541 --> 19:06.544
Everything's alright,
everything'll be okay.

19:06.546 --> 19:10.681
- This wood, this lumber,
where did it come from?

19:11.750 --> 19:13.151
- That's just left over.

19:13.153 --> 19:16.454
Scraps from the floor
renovations, why?

19:18.357 --> 19:19.690
- I don't know.

19:20.459 --> 19:22.660
- Enough of this, come on.

19:22.662 --> 19:24.896
I'll fix us some dinner.

20:22.988 --> 20:25.489
- Yeah, that'll fit the bill.

20:26.291 --> 20:28.292
Side door, easy access.

20:32.664 --> 20:36.734
Looks like a nice,
white-bread, mid-class joint.

21:59.051 --> 21:59.917
- Boo!

21:59.919 --> 22:01.352
- Goddammit!

22:01.354 --> 22:03.454
What are you trying to do,
give me a heart attack?

22:03.456 --> 22:05.089
- I just stopped by to see Amy.

22:05.091 --> 22:05.990
Mind?

22:06.892 --> 22:09.694
- I guess not,
she's in the pool.

22:11.496 --> 22:12.463
Stupid kid.

22:21.106 --> 22:23.174
- Hey, what are you doing here?

22:23.176 --> 22:24.508
- Just thought I'd stop by
and visit.

22:24.510 --> 22:25.710
Mind?

22:25.712 --> 22:26.544
- No.

22:26.546 --> 22:28.112
But my dad won't be happy.

22:28.114 --> 22:30.114
- I just startled him.

22:30.116 --> 22:32.283
- He just hasn't
been himself lately.

22:32.285 --> 22:34.885
- Oh, he'll get over it.

22:34.887 --> 22:36.420
Parents.

22:36.422 --> 22:38.289
- Hey, could you chill here
a minute?

22:38.291 --> 22:39.724
I'm gonna go do some laps.

22:39.726 --> 22:40.891
- Sure thing.

23:10.455 --> 23:11.355
Ah!

23:42.555 --> 23:44.688
- Hey, are you okay?

23:44.690 --> 23:46.690
Did you swallow some water?

23:46.692 --> 23:48.826
- Didn't you see or hear?

23:49.761 --> 23:52.797
- You just swam a couple
laps and came back.

23:52.799 --> 23:54.698
- Something pulled me!

23:56.201 --> 23:57.668
- Dinner's ready.

24:31.204 --> 24:32.603
Hello?

24:32.605 --> 24:32.603
- Hello.

24:32.605 --> 24:35.739
It's urgent I speak
with Jeremy dukane.

24:35.741 --> 24:37.141
This is father benna.

24:37.143 --> 24:38.242
- This is him.

24:38.244 --> 24:39.510
What do you want?

24:39.512 --> 24:42.780
Why are you church folks always
trying to solicit people?

24:42.782 --> 24:43.948
- You don't understand.

24:43.950 --> 24:44.915
This has to do with your--

24:44.917 --> 24:48.052
- whatever it is,
I'm not interested.

24:52.958 --> 24:54.225
- Who was that?

24:54.227 --> 24:57.561
- Some religious nut trying
to solicit money or something.

24:57.563 --> 24:59.530
- And you don't believe
in charity?

24:59.532 --> 25:00.698
- Yeah, mine.

25:07.874 --> 25:09.206
- Amy.

25:09.208 --> 25:11.175
You still freaked out
by the pool?

25:11.177 --> 25:13.511
- What about the pool?

25:13.513 --> 25:15.079
- Uh, something...

25:18.216 --> 25:20.651
I just got caught in something.

25:20.653 --> 25:22.720
- I have to check the
suction on the filter.

25:22.722 --> 25:25.789
Might be high and you got
caught in the backflow.

25:25.791 --> 25:28.392
- No, it wasn't that, it was...

25:36.468 --> 25:38.536
It was nothing, I guess.

25:41.439 --> 25:44.475
- So, robby,
did you get a job yet?

25:44.477 --> 25:45.776
Or are you gonna
waste away the summer?

25:45.778 --> 25:47.378
- No.

25:47.380 --> 25:49.647
I have a job working at
my dad's hardware store

25:49.649 --> 25:51.282
and I'm gonna save up money
for college.

25:51.284 --> 25:52.650
- Great.

25:52.652 --> 25:55.653
Education is a terrible thing
to waste.

25:55.655 --> 25:58.989
- Well, speaking of work,
i gotta get going.

25:58.991 --> 26:00.224
See ya 'round.

26:02.460 --> 26:04.261
- I'll walk with you.

26:05.697 --> 26:08.265
- You, you gonna be okay?

26:08.267 --> 26:09.433
- Yeah, fine.

26:10.835 --> 26:12.469
Call me later?

26:12.471 --> 26:14.872
- Yeah, you can count on it.

28:50.995 --> 28:52.396
- Business time.

29:49.687 --> 29:50.921
What the hell?

32:28.813 --> 32:29.713
- Amy?

32:40.925 --> 32:42.326
Amy, what is it?

33:29.541 --> 33:31.842
- In the name of god,
who are you?

33:31.844 --> 33:34.311
- You are foolish,
like your brother.

33:34.313 --> 33:35.746
Stop your folly now,

33:35.748 --> 33:37.814
or suffer the torments of hell.

33:37.816 --> 33:39.116
- Never! Never!

33:40.351 --> 33:43.353
I plan on finishing
what my brother started.

33:43.355 --> 33:46.923
- You have determination,
but it won't be enough.

33:46.925 --> 33:48.258
We are many.

33:48.260 --> 33:49.860
We are powerful.

33:49.862 --> 33:51.461
We are forever.

33:51.463 --> 33:54.831
- And I have the strength
and blood of the almighty!

33:54.833 --> 33:56.366
- Do not challenge me with your

33:56.368 --> 33:58.702
pious traditions and beliefs.

33:58.704 --> 34:00.270
We have a great work to finish

34:00.272 --> 34:02.372
and you will not interfere!

34:02.374 --> 34:05.909
- The only thing
i have to finish is you!

34:05.911 --> 34:07.844
What is your name?

34:07.846 --> 34:09.746
I command you!

34:13.819 --> 34:14.717
Your name!

34:26.331 --> 34:30.000
- Hey, what's going on
in there?

34:40.777 --> 34:42.344
- Hey, Amy.

34:42.347 --> 34:44.313
Uh, how's it going?

34:44.315 --> 34:46.315
- Fine, robby, and you?

34:48.553 --> 34:52.522
- Uh, well, um my dad needs
me to work this afternoon,

34:52.524 --> 34:55.257
so I won't be able to come over.

34:55.260 --> 34:56.493
Maybe tonight?

34:57.328 --> 34:58.995
- We'll see, robby.

35:00.698 --> 35:01.765
We will see.

35:04.235 --> 35:06.236
- Are uh, are you okay?

35:07.305 --> 35:09.439
Sound a little different.

35:10.374 --> 35:11.908
- Tired.

35:11.910 --> 35:13.477
Just tired, robby.

35:15.179 --> 35:17.747
- Your dad hasn't been
hassling you again, has he?

35:17.749 --> 35:19.216
- No.

35:19.218 --> 35:20.550
He's somewhere.

35:22.053 --> 35:23.286
Maybe outside.

35:24.322 --> 35:25.455
- Well, okay.

35:26.958 --> 35:28.959
Sounds like you're eating lunch?

35:28.961 --> 35:30.861
- A snack, that's all.

35:32.497 --> 35:33.997
Talk to ya later.

35:57.488 --> 35:59.422
- Where do you think
you're going?

35:59.424 --> 36:01.224
- For a walk.

36:01.226 --> 36:02.692
- Help me out, first.

36:02.694 --> 36:04.427
- I don't have time.

36:05.496 --> 36:07.197
- What did you say?

36:15.306 --> 36:17.707
You don't be long now, hear?

37:21.038 --> 37:22.539
Can I help you?

37:22.541 --> 37:24.774
- Mr. Jeremy dukane?

37:24.776 --> 37:26.142
- Yah, that's me.

37:26.144 --> 37:27.711
- We need to talk.

37:30.314 --> 37:33.149
- You called me yesterday,
didn't you?

37:33.151 --> 37:35.585
- Yes, I was trying to warn you.

37:35.587 --> 37:36.786
- Warn me?

37:36.788 --> 37:38.455
About what?

37:38.457 --> 37:41.224
- You and your family
may be in great danger.

37:41.226 --> 37:42.125
- How so?

37:43.394 --> 37:45.862
- Have you noticed
anything strange going on,

37:45.864 --> 37:48.765
with your family or yourself?

37:48.767 --> 37:52.435
- It's only my daughter
and I who live here.

37:52.437 --> 37:53.837
My wife is gone.

37:56.641 --> 37:59.709
- Anything at all
out of the ordinary?

37:59.711 --> 38:02.078
- What business is it of yours?

38:02.080 --> 38:04.547
- So, there have been issues?

38:05.783 --> 38:08.852
- My daughter acts a
little weird sometimes,

38:08.854 --> 38:10.854
but it's just kid stuff, though.

38:10.856 --> 38:12.088
- Interesting.

38:12.090 --> 38:12.989
Recently?

38:14.091 --> 38:15.959
- In the last few days.

38:15.961 --> 38:16.860
Why?

38:17.862 --> 38:21.364
- Does the name Charles humes
ring a bell?

38:21.366 --> 38:25.001
- Yeah, he did some work
on the floors.

38:25.003 --> 38:26.569
Bad luck about

38:26.571 --> 38:28.905
his murdering his wife
and daughters.

38:34.780 --> 38:37.781
Seemed perfectly normal to me.

38:37.783 --> 38:41.651
- Most people are until
they become possessed.

38:41.653 --> 38:42.719
- Possessed?

38:43.587 --> 38:46.056
What are you getting at?

38:46.058 --> 38:49.359
- Charles worked on the
original amityville house.

38:49.361 --> 38:50.360
- So what?

38:50.362 --> 38:52.696
Those stories are crap.

38:52.698 --> 38:54.064
There's a family who lives
in there now

38:54.066 --> 38:56.399
who seems perfectly happy.

38:56.401 --> 39:00.070
There's no media sensations
about ghosts or goblins.

39:00.072 --> 39:03.106
- That's because my brother
exorcised the house,

39:03.108 --> 39:05.675
before he was thrown from
the window and killed.

39:05.677 --> 39:06.576
- Ah!

39:08.213 --> 39:11.915
- I heard about that accident
a while ago.

39:11.917 --> 39:12.816
I'm sorry.

39:13.751 --> 39:15.785
But what does this have to do
with me?

39:15.787 --> 39:17.320
My house?

39:17.322 --> 39:19.889
- Charles did work
on your floors.

39:19.891 --> 39:21.591
He took lumber
from the amityville house

39:21.593 --> 39:24.327
and used it on your renovations.

39:25.529 --> 39:26.363
- So?

39:26.365 --> 39:28.665
Good lumber is hard to find.

39:28.667 --> 39:32.302
- Have you ever heard
of evil transference?

39:33.437 --> 39:35.038
Let's go inside.

39:35.040 --> 39:37.774
We'll discuss it in more detail.

40:22.987 --> 40:25.555
Did you have a party recently?

40:26.957 --> 40:29.125
- Yeah, me, myself and I.

40:31.929 --> 40:34.330
- Thanks for the coffee.

40:34.332 --> 40:35.999
Now, as I was saying,

40:36.001 --> 40:38.134
evil transference.

40:38.136 --> 40:39.769
- Yeah, what is it?

40:41.005 --> 40:43.473
What does it have to do with me?

40:43.475 --> 40:46.176
- I strongly sense and
believe that the evil

40:46.178 --> 40:48.378
in that house attached
itself to the materials

40:48.380 --> 40:52.015
brought here and could
have been set loose.

40:54.285 --> 40:55.952
- Set loose?

40:55.954 --> 40:57.287
How?

40:57.289 --> 41:01.224
- Demons and evil thrive
on discord intention.

41:01.226 --> 41:03.460
Is there any of that
in your home?

41:03.462 --> 41:06.129
- Yeah, for quite a while, now.

41:07.498 --> 41:10.633
My wife was killed in a
drunk driving accident

41:10.635 --> 41:13.870
and my daughter
has never forgiven me.

41:14.805 --> 41:17.807
- Why does she need
to forgive you?

41:19.210 --> 41:21.377
- I was the drunk driver.

41:23.948 --> 41:24.848
- I see.

41:27.184 --> 41:30.186
To further explain,
Charles humes took building

41:30.188 --> 41:33.456
materials and used them
on his house, as well.

41:33.458 --> 41:34.924
He confessed to me
that that's when

41:34.926 --> 41:37.293
he was driven
to kill his family.

41:37.295 --> 41:39.729
That he was possessed
and it started

41:39.731 --> 41:43.299
when he introduced the
lumber into his home.

41:43.301 --> 41:46.803
Do you have any leftover
pieces of the material?

41:46.805 --> 41:48.872
- Yeah, in the basement.

41:56.481 --> 41:58.214
- What are you doing?

41:58.216 --> 42:00.884
- Uh, just taking your picture.

42:01.819 --> 42:03.887
Beauty in nature, I'll call it.

42:03.889 --> 42:06.990
- Don't you think
you should ask first?

42:06.992 --> 42:09.893
- Okay, mind if I take
your photo?

42:12.129 --> 42:13.530
- Sure, why not?

42:14.565 --> 42:15.698
But not here.

42:17.501 --> 42:20.870
Over there, away from the road.

42:20.872 --> 42:22.038
- Yeah, sure.

42:23.007 --> 42:26.175
