to help?

45:41.139 --> 45:43.005
- This situation
was ordained before

45:43.007 --> 45:45.742
we were a twinkle in time's eye.

45:46.710 --> 45:49.879
The evil is after your daughter,

45:49.881 --> 45:53.516
because she is young,
malleable, persuaded.

45:54.585 --> 45:55.752
Where is she?

45:57.020 --> 46:01.057
