46:43.700 --> 46:46.502
- No offense,
but he's also dead.

47:20.370 --> 47:22.104
Don't be afraid, Amy.

47:22.106 --> 47:23.739
This is father benna.

47:23.741 --> 47:24.774
He's an old high-school friend

47:24.776 --> 47:26.676
