in the neighborhood.

47:26.678 --> 47:28.477
He's gonna be staying a day
or two.

47:28.479 --> 47:30.112
- Nice to meet you.

47:33.283 --> 47:36.219
- You never finished
high school.

47:36.221 --> 47:39.055
And I never knew you
to have friends,

47:39.057 --> 47:40.790
especially a priest.

47:42.960 --> 47:46.262
- Yes, we even grew up
in the same neighborhood.

47:46.264 --> 47:47.163
- Cute.

47:48.031 --> 47:49.765
If you'll excuse me.

48:04.848 --> 48:05.748
Help me.

48:08.887 --> 48:09.785
Help me.

48:11.588 --> 48:12.889
There is a holy
shaman in the house.

48:18.762 --> 48:19.929
He is strong.

49:29.333 --> 49:30.700
- What's in here?

49:30.702 --> 49:32.001
- It's a workspace.

49:32.003 --> 49:34.837
My wife used to make
decorative boxes in there.

49:34.839 --> 49:37.106
