to encounter.

50:09.440 --> 50:11.574
Let's keep going.

50:38.870 --> 50:40.169
- Hello?

50:40.171 --> 50:41.003
- Hey, there.

50:41.005 --> 50:42.471
Feeling any better?

50:42.473 --> 50:43.539
- I suppose.

50:45.876 --> 50:47.143
- You sure?

50:47.145 --> 50:49.445
