50:49.447 --> 50:50.546
Can I come by later?

50:50.548 --> 50:51.447
- No.

50:54.851 --> 50:58.054
- Don't, don't you want
to see me?

50:58.056 --> 50:59.655
- It's not that.

50:59.657 --> 51:03.092
My father has a friend here
visiting.

51:03.094 --> 51:04.860
I have an idea.

51:04.862 --> 51:07.563
Why don't I sneak out
and meet you?

51:07.565 --> 51:09.365
- Okay, yeah, yeah.

51:09.367 --> 51:11.667
What's the time and place?

51:11.669 --> 51:13.102
- In an hour.

51:13.104 --> 51:16.806
Park your car
at the old recreation field.

51:16.808 --> 51:18.240
I'll be there.

51:18.242 --> 51:19.675
- Okay, sounds like a plan.

51:19.677 --> 51:21.477
See you then.

51:35.692 --> 51:37.359
- Well, that should do it.

51:37.361 --> 51:39.128
The entire perimeter
and the foundations

51:39.130 --> 51:42.631
