and blanketed in prayer.

51:50.408 --> 51:52.341
- Will that help?

51:52.343 --> 51:54.110
- It will help keep the
evil from escaping once

51:54.112 --> 51:56.145
we begin the exorcism.

51:56.147 --> 51:58.247
- Isn't that what we want it
to do?

52:03.520 --> 52:04.854
- No.

52:04.856 --> 52:07.990
We want to stop it and
send it back to hell.

52:09.227 --> 52:12.394
- Is there really such a place?

52:12.396 --> 52:16.332
- Yes, just like there
is a place called heaven.

52:16.334 --> 52:19.068
We make our own hell and our own
heaven.

52:19.070 --> 52:20.603
We simply have to decide which
one

52:20.605 --> 52:23.839
we will step into when our time
comes.

52:45.629 --> 52:47.830
- When are we going to
perform this exorcism?

52:47.832 --> 52:49.365
- When the time is right.

52:49.367 --> 52:50.833
Possibly tonight.

52:50.835 --> 52:52.535
Maybe tomorrow.

52:52.537 --> 52:54.036
Trust me, Jeremy.

52:55.138 --> 52:56.038
- I, I do.

52:57.908 --> 53:00.276
She'll be okay afterwards,
right?

53:00.278 --> 53:02.711
- She'll be back to normal.

53:02.713 --> 53:04.180
- I'll take that.

53:05.248 --> 53:09.618
What are we gonna use to
fight against this evil?

53:09.620 --> 53:12.721
- Our wits, our strength,
our faith

53:12.723 --> 53:14.790
and our courage.

53:14.792 --> 53:17.927
- Running low
on all those ingredients.

53:17.929 --> 53:20.362
- When the time comes,
you'll find all of them.

53:20.364 --> 53:24.500
You have to, for your
daughter's sake, and yours.

53:25.268 --> 53:26.468
Let's get something to eat
and then we'll

53:26.470 --> 53:29.038
bless the inside of the house.

53:46.624 --> 53:47.456
- Come on.

53:47.458 --> 53:49.358
What's taking so long?

53:55.498 --> 53:56.398
What?

54:04.274 --> 54:05.107
- Ah!

54:05.109 --> 54:06.008
- Jesus!

54:20.758 --> 54:24.159
Damn, you scared the hell
out of me!

54:24.161 --> 54:29.765
- Did i
scare the hell out of you?

54:29.767 --> 54:33.202
- Yeah, that's what
i just said--

54:33.204 --> 54:35.871
- I mean the real hell.

54:35.873 --> 54:38.107
Did I scare it out of you?

54:39.976 --> 54:42.611
- What, what's gotten into you?

54:42.613 --> 54:43.512
- Him.

55:25.856 --> 55:26.755
- Ah!

55:31.795 --> 55:32.695
Ah!

55:50.780 --> 55:52.247
- Where'd she go?

55:53.350 --> 55:54.850
Where is she?

56:26.649 --> 56:28.751
Where've you been?

56:28.753 --> 56:30.552
- I don't feel so good.

56:30.554 --> 56:32.588
- Let's get her upstairs.

57:01.851 --> 57:03.685
- I don't like the idea
of tying her up.

57:03.687 --> 57:05.621
It's, it's agonizing.

57:05.623 --> 57:07.289
It's cruel.

57:07.291 --> 57:09.858
- If we don't, she may
escape and harm someone,

57:09.860 --> 57:12.594
or herself,
is that what you want?

57:12.596 --> 57:13.929
- Of course not.

57:13.931 --> 57:15.197
- Then we must do it.

57:15.199 --> 57:17.466
We can't afford for her
to get away from us.

57:17.468 --> 57:18.700
- Won't blessing the whole house

57:18.702 --> 57:20.369
keep her confined?

57:20.371 --> 57:23.372
- It will help,
but it isn't a given.

57:23.374 --> 57:26.141
You saw how she weakened when
she stepped inside earlier.

57:26.143 --> 57:27.576
That's a good sign.

57:27.578 --> 57:29.344
We may have the upper hand.

57:29.346 --> 57:31.680
- Then let's get on with
it and get it over with.

57:31.682 --> 57:33.048
- You must be patient.

57:33.050 --> 57:34.550
When the time is right.

57:34.552 --> 57:37.686
- How will know
when it is the right time?

57:37.688 --> 57:39.087
- You'll know.

59:45.415 --> 59:46.315
- Ah!

59:47.650 --> 59:48.483
- No!

59:56.426 --> 59:57.559
How did you--

01:00:04.067 --> 01:00:05.300
- you bastard!

01:00:06.803 --> 01:00:08.370
You filthy priest!

01:00:09.706 --> 01:00:10.706
Go to hell!

01:00:11.541 --> 01:00:13.909
