01:07:03.252 --> 01:07:04.152
Drunk!

01:07:05.087 --> 01:07:05.987
Killer!

01:07:06.822 --> 01:07:09.124
Mommy killer! Mommy killer!

01:07:11.927 --> 01:07:13.595
- Shut up, shut up!

01:07:14.363 --> 01:07:17.165
