from your holy place

01:09:37.407 --> 01:09:40.241
and watch over her from Zion.

01:09:40.243 --> 01:09:42.176
Lord, heed my prayer

01:09:42.179 --> 01:09:45.013
and let my cry be heard by you.

01:09:46.683 --> 01:09:48.616
