01:10:52.481 --> 01:10:55.116
- I want you to meet my father.

01:11:07.196 --> 01:11:08.663
- Open this door!

01:11:09.898 --> 01:11:11.266
Let me in.

01:11:13.270 --> 01:11:14.902
Don't hurt my baby.

01:11:14.904 --> 01:11:16.271
- It's over, priest.

